It is already possible to set a specific assignee for a via-email-created issue with the "CC Assignee"-flag. (_CreateOrCommentHandler_)

This is not really intuitive for the user, as the CC field is also used to add watchers to the issue.

It would be better to use the first "To"-Email found (of course only emails different to the catch-email-address).
In case there is more than 1 additional "To"-email-address, these user(s) should become watcher(s) too.

*Usage example*:
To: {catchemail}, {Assignee}, {Watcher1}, {Watcher2}
CC: {Watcher3}, {Watcher4}...
